 {'from': 'human', 'value': 'Looking back, I think my addiction began as a way to cope with unresolved trauma from my childhood. I experienced a lot of pain and loss, and at that time, turning to substances seemed like the only solution. However, I now see that it has only added another layer of pain to my life.'}
